description: Extract from FEAR IN MOTION (2019, cinegraph) . 1080x1080.png . FEAR IN MOTION is an experimental short film of a singular choreography between a photographer and a dancer which illuminates some 2541 animated “freeze on photographs” captured during the rehearsals of FEAR AND GREED by Frédérick Gravel at Usine C.
